3. terminal look
	terminal preferences - profile - scrolling - uncheck "show scrollbar"
	sudo apt install gnome-shell-extension-pixelsaver
    gnome-extensions enable pixel-saver@deadalnix.me
    gsettings set org.gnome.Terminal.Legacy.Settings headerbar false


    shift right click can toggle options in tmux

4. remove dock

gnome-extensions disable ubuntu-dock@ubuntu.com

5. remove top bar
   https://extensions.gnome.org/ 
   search hide top bar by tuxor1337
   install firefox extension and activate

